        <div type="footnotes">
            <note xml:id="foot.f1">The date range is established from the fact that the content of the letter relates to CD’s work on expression (see n. 2, below). CD was working on expression with a view to publishing between 1867 and 1872.</note>
            <note xml:id="foot.f2">CD cited this passage in <hi rend="italic">Expression</hi>, p. 323. See also the letters from F. J. Wedgwood to H. E. Darwin, <ref target="./DCP-LETT-7058.xml">[1867–72]</ref> and <ref target="./DCP-LETT-7059.xml">[1867–72]</ref> (in this Supplement). The passage is from <hi rend="italic">Ad Lucilium epistulae morales</hi> 11: 7, with some words omitted.</note>
